        prerequisites
        =============
        
        Python 2 or Python 3
        --------------------
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            sudo apt-get -y install python
            sudo apt-get -y install python3
        
        matplotlib
        ----------
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            sudo apt-get -y install python-matplotlib
            sudo apt-get -y install python3-matplotlib
        
